## Add A Machine

1. Add SSH alias to `~/.ssh/config`.
2. Run key setup from station repo.
3. Verify `ssh -o BatchMode=yes <alias> 'uname -m; sw_vers -productVersion'`.
4. Record reboot/autologin behavior.
5. Mark which tests are allowed.
